 (x+h)^n=\sum_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}x^kh^{n-k}, 
 \frac{a(x+h)^n-ax^n}{h}=\frac{a}{h}\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\binom{n}{k}x^kh^{n-k}=a\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\binom{n}{k}x^kh^{n-k-1}. 
(x+h)^n=\sum_{m=0}^nc(n,m)x^mh^{n-m}
c(n,m)=\frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}
